* 1942-1945{{spaced ndash}}    {{nihongo|Bandung Epidemics Institute|バンドン防疫研究所|Bandon Bōeki Kenkyūsho}}, under [[Japanese occupation of the Dutch East Indies|Japanese occupation]]
* 1945-1949 {{spaced ndash}}   {{lang|id|Gedung Cacar dan Lembaga Pasteur}}, after Indonesian independence. During the [[Indonesian National Revolution|independence war]], its activities moved to [[Klaten]], [[Yogyakarta]]
